for the Empire of Japan.

00:29:52.590 --> 00:29:54.500
We shouldn't stress over these things.

00:29:55.280 --> 00:29:57.810
If that's what you came to talk about,

00:29:58.480 --> 00:30:02.770
there's no need to bother the Colonel.

00:30:03.000 --> 00:30:04.980
You could've told me directly.

00:30:06.790 --> 00:30:07.570
Besides,

00:30:07.590 --> 00:30:08.570
this checkup

00:30:08.590 --> 00:30:11.290
is really for your own good.

00:30:11.760 --> 00:30:12.700
For my own good?

00:30:15.590 --> 00:30:17.050
I honestly don't get it.

00:30:17.830 --> 00:30:19.850
Mr. Takeda, if you mean well,

00:30:20.070 --> 00:30:21.740
why risk my safety

00:30:21.760 --> 00:30:23.500
and make me go through
that invasive test?

