Takeda, you personally
moved the Navy in.

00:30:48.070 --> 00:30:48.850
That's enough!

00:30:53.310 --> 00:30:54.330
Mr. Lee.

00:30:54.870 --> 00:30:56.850
Don't believe those rumors.

00:30:56.870 --> 00:30:58.530
I really had no idea before,

00:30:58.550 --> 00:31:00.500
this checkup could actually do harm.

00:31:00.590 --> 00:31:02.090
Now I get it.

00:31:03.000 --> 00:31:04.740
If you're not up for it,

00:31:04.760 --> 00:31:06.530
then let's just skip the exam.

00:31:07.280 --> 00:31:09.330
We'll wait for Dr. Miyamoto.

