I can't get through to you.

00:31:13.000 --> 00:31:13.850
I need to see the Colonel.

00:31:28.830 --> 00:31:29.770
Sorry to interrupt, I'm coming in.

00:31:35.240 --> 00:31:36.050
Where's the Colonel?

