With all these chlorpheniramine,

00:36:03.230 --> 00:36:05.210
I'll manage that exam tomorrow.

00:36:08.480 --> 00:36:09.820
Hopefully you won't need it.

00:36:15.790 --> 00:36:16.770
Ms. Xian,

00:36:18.560 --> 00:36:20.610
don't just keep staring at me.

00:36:21.790 --> 00:36:24.610
I know I look pretty bad right now,

00:36:27.000 --> 00:36:28.820
but it's nothing serious,

00:36:29.480 --> 00:36:30.980
just a little itchy, really.

00:36:31.840 --> 00:36:33.170
I'll be fine in a couple of days.

00:36:33.190 --> 00:36:35.610
I won't be an eyesore for long.

