First, he linked up with the British,

00:40:29.520 --> 00:40:33.020
pretending to train our cipher talent.

00:40:34.480 --> 00:40:35.460
Then, he used Xian Biyun

00:40:35.480 --> 00:40:38.570
to sell our intel to the British.

00:40:39.480 --> 00:40:41.060
Now he's done selling

00:40:41.080 --> 00:40:43.170
and planned to sneak away
on a British merchant ship.

00:40:45.150 --> 00:40:47.610
It's not that easy.

00:40:52.190 --> 00:40:53.250
Alright.

00:40:54.590 --> 00:40:56.170
Tonight's the night.

00:40:56.190 --> 00:40:57.730
We'll catch them with everything.

00:40:59.400 --> 00:41:00.650
Just heard from someone,

00:41:00.920 --> 00:41:04.610
Charlie stole a doctor's uniform
from the laundry,

00:41:04.670 --> 00:41:07.900
clearly prepping
for the escape tonight.

00:41:07.920 --> 00:41:09.090
I've checked myself.

00:41:09.110 --> 00:41:11.130
