stored in the pharmacy,

00:41:11.590 --> 00:41:13.500
I'll find a way to set it alight.

00:41:13.920 --> 00:41:15.020
You run off during the chaos.

00:41:15.520 --> 00:41:17.980
I'll meet you at our spot.

