Set our main team outside the hospital.

00:41:54.670 --> 00:41:55.380
Even if Joseph Lee

00:41:55.400 --> 00:41:57.380
comes out from the sewer,

00:41:58.000 --> 00:42:00.570
someone must be on him right away.

00:42:00.920 --> 00:42:01.980
At the same time,

00:42:02.630 --> 00:42:05.690
I'll secure the roads
from the hospital to the dock

00:42:05.710 --> 00:42:07.250
all covered.

