Once he boards KLX83,

00:42:11.040 --> 00:42:12.900
and when the ship moves,

00:42:13.480 --> 00:42:15.090
that's when we move in.

00:42:15.110 --> 00:42:16.380
As long as he gets on the ship

00:42:16.400 --> 00:42:17.500
and meets up with Frank,

00:42:17.520 --> 00:42:19.460
we can hold them right away.

